OL,3,CUS-Iran deal: What we are witnessing
OL,4,Cis how to sell defeat as victory
OL,6,FSo, the much-discussed deal between
OL,7,Fthe United States and Iran is almost a
OL,8,Freality.
OL,10,FThe torturous process, which began
OL,11,Fwhen a ceasefire was agreed in April,
OL,12,Fis due to be officially signed on
OL,13,FFriday in Geneva.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
