OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781511482
OL,3,CUS-Iran deal: What we are witnessing
OL,4,Cis how to sell defeat as victory
OL,6,FPresident Trump, who has said it was
OL,7,Fimminent around 40 times in recent
OL,8,Fweeks, almost got his 80th birthday
OL,9,Fwish, not the signatures he had
OL,10,Fsought, but at least a public
OL,11,Facknowledgement of a 60-day extension
OL,12,Fof the ceasefire and the reopening of
OL,13,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,15,FPresident Trump is selling this as a
OL,16,Fwin, but it is far from that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
