OL,3,CUS-Iran deal: What we are witnessing
OL,4,Cis how to sell defeat as victory
OL,6,FIt's an agreement which he desperately
OL,7,Fhopes will solve some of the chaos
OL,8,Fcaused by the war in Iran, which he
OL,9,Fchose to start. Getting the strait
OL,10,Fopen is critical to the global
OL,11,Feconomy, energy and markets.
OL,13,FFor a man who talks about his great
OL,14,Fdeal-making skills, this is more an
OL,15,Fexercise in capitulation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
