CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781511482
OL,3,CUS-Iran deal: What we are witnessing
OL,4,Cis how to sell defeat as victory
OL,6,FHe's now been forced to offer multiple
OL,7,Fconcessions and a lot of cash to the
OL,8,FIranian rulers he sought to overthrow
OL,9,Fwhen he started this war. They
OL,10,Foutwitted him, and this is the
OL,11,Fconsequence.
OL,13,FNow the really hard work will need to
OL,14,Fbegin with thorny discussions about
OL,15,FIran's nuclear ambitions, what happens
OL,16,Fto its existing stockpile of enriched
OL,17,Furanium, and what sanctions relief
OL,18,Fwill be on offer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
