OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781511482
OL,3,CUS-Iran deal: What we are witnessing
OL,4,Cis how to sell defeat as victory
OL,6,FThen there's the question of Lebanon -
OL,7,Fthe Iranians say they will only go
OL,8,Fforward with the 60 days of talks if
OL,9,Fthere's an end to fighting across all
OL,10,Ffronts.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThat is not entirely in President
OL,18,FTrump's gift, as Israel's attack on
OL,19,FBeirut yesterday proved once more.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
