OL,3,CUS-Iran deal: What we are witnessing
OL,4,Cis how to sell defeat as victory
OL,6,FFor sure this deal will not be
OL,7,Fwelcomed by the Israeli Prime
OL,8,FMinister, how far he goes to
OL,9,Fjeopardise it will prove critical in
OL,10,Fthe days ahead. This could prove to be
OL,11,Fa very long and jittery week.
OL,13,FThat some progress has been made is
OL,14,Fgood, if it can be properly followed
OL,15,Fthrough a longer term deal would save
OL,16,Flives on all fronts, a reopening of
OL,17,Fthe strait would bring energy and fuel
OL,18,Fprices down and give the global
OL,19,Feconomy chance to recover.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
