OL,3,CUS-Iran deal: What we are witnessing
OL,4,Cis how to sell defeat as victory
OL,6,FBut none of those three issues were at
OL,7,Fplay before this war began.
OL,9,FWhat we are witnessing is how to sell
OL,10,Fdefeat as victory.
OL,12,FIf this doesn't work we will all pay
OL,13,Fthe price, literally and
OL,14,Fmetaphorically.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
